manifests.contents:
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "playmatch"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "playmatch"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
build = "build.rs"
authors = ["DevYukine <devyukine@gmx.de>"]
description = "A simple matchmaking service"

[workspace]
members = [".", "api", "service", "entity", "migration"]

[dependencies.api]
path = "api"

[build-dependencies]
built = "^0.7"

bin = []
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[package]
name = "api"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
build = "build.rs"

[dependencies]
actix-governor = "0.5.0"
actix-web = "^4"
anyhow = "^1.0"
chrono = "^0.4"
dotenvy = "^0.15"
env_logger = "^0.11"
log = "^0.4"
num_cpus = "^1.16"
serde_derive = "^1"
serde_json = "^1"
serde_repr = "^0.1"
thiserror = "^1"
uuid = "^1.10"

[dependencies.entity]
path = "../entity"

[dependencies.migration]
path = "../migration"

[dependencies.reqwest]
version = "^0.12"
features = ["rustls-tls", "json"]
default-features = false

[dependencies.sea-orm]
version = "0.12"
features = ["sqlx-postgres", "runtime-tokio-rustls", "macros", "with-chrono", "with-uuid"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "^1"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.service]
path = "../service"

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "^1"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.utoipa]
version = "4.2.3"
features = ["actix_extras", "uuid", "chrono"]

[dependencies.utoipa-swagger-ui]
version = "7.1.0"
features = ["actix-web"]

[build-dependencies]
built = "^0.7"

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "api"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2021"
required-features = []
crate-type = ["rlib"]

bin = []
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[package]
name = "entity"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"

[dependencies]
chrono = "^0.4"
serde = "^1"

[dependencies.sea-orm]
version = "0.12"

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "entity"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2021"
required-features = []
crate-type = ["rlib"]

bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "migration"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "migration"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
publish = false

[dependencies.async-std]
version = "1"
features = ["attributes", "tokio1"]

[dependencies.sea-orm-migration]
version = "0.12.0"
features = ["runtime-tokio-rustls", "sqlx-postgres"]

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "migration"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
required-features = []

bin = []
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[package]
name = "service"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"

[dependencies.entity]
path = "../entity"

[dependencies.sea-orm]
version = "^0.12"
features = ["debug-print", "runtime-tokio-rustls", "sqlx-postgres"]

[dev-dependencies.tokio]
version = "^1"
features = ["macros", "rt"]

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "service"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2021"
required-features = []
crate-type = ["rlib"]
